<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，天上出现了黑色的乌云。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天上下起了暴雨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波涛汹涌，就像是高高的黑山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，真好玩儿！”小美人鱼想，“暴风雨来了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在海底王国，即使暴风雨来了，她和她的姐姐们也很安全。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们喜欢在汹涌的海水里玩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50139</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，船员们很害怕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50140</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们拉住绳子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子的船开始摇动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>船在暴雨中摇晃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>船摇晃得越来越厉害。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所有船员们都到甲板上来！”一个船员大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73938</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“船要沉了！”另一个船员大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼不害怕，她在远处等着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在黑暗中，她看着船想：“我真幸运！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在王子不能离开了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也许早上前我能再见他一面。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95198</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼并不知道船陷入了危险。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102483</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>暴风雨越来越厉害。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102484</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巨大的波涛拍打着甲板。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105973</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>风吹着船帆，把船帆撕开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，主桅杆突然破裂掉进了水里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>船一倾斜，海水就灌进了甲板。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125612</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“放下救生艇！”一个船员大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127777</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们必须救乘客！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，已经太晚了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一道闪电击中船，一股狂风吹灭了所有的灯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，四周黑了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，又一道闪电击中，船起火了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>船开始燃烧起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150825</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在闪电下，小美人鱼看见人类在求生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不。”她担心地说，“可怜的人类！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165114</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一些人掉进了海里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169258</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另一些人从着火的甲板上往下跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169259</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“救命！救命！”人们尖叫着掉进水里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175338</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181556</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼看见那个戴着蓝色羽毛的女人抱着一个桌子腿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181557</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个男人拼命向海边游去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“救命！”一个客人大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不想死！”另一个客人大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有人都拼命让头浮在水面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼拼命地找王子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205256</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于，她看见了王子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205257</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209674</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在努力挣扎，可是他太累了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209675</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他开始往下沉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他要去访问海底王国！”小美人鱼开心地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，她记起来人类不能在海底生活。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227159</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人类和人鱼不一样，人类不能在水里呼吸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227160</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234027</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的王子会死的！哦，我必须去救他！”她担心地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234028</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼向破碎的船游过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拼命地游。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，她发现了快沉下去的王子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她游到了王子身边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253606</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看起来像一片从树上掉下来的叶子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253607</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼抓住他，把他的头托到了水上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“加油，亲爱的王子，你安全了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在他的耳边小声地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她顺着波涛游到了海边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>